{
  "texts": [
    "The center band of the Hα line for calculating the correlation coefficients between the spectra is indicated by a shaded area in orange in Figure 18a.",
    "The variation of the evaluated correlation coefficients with the sequence numbers of the spectra (sorted by I Hα index) is shown in Figure 18b.",
    "Because the spectrum No.",
    "0 is used as the reference spectrum relative to which the correlation coefficients of other spectra are calculated, it does not appear in the plot in Figure 18b.",
    "The consistency of the Hα profiles in the line center is judged by the minimum value of the evaluated correlation coefficients between the spectra (indicated by a circle symbol in Figure 18b)."
  ]
}